# Session 5 Handover — Fumage

## What was built this session

### /dupes page + nav link
A new browsable dupes page at `/dupes` lists every fragrance in the database that has known cheaper alternatives. Originals are ordered by popularity score, each rendered as a section header. Below each header, dupe cards show the source fragrance name (linked), house, price tier, similarity badge (color-coded: amber = close clone, sky = strong similarity, stone = partial), price note, and editorial notes.

`src/app/dupes/page.tsx` — server component, Prisma query.
`src/components/nav/Nav.tsx` — "Dupes" link added between Notes and Guide.

### 13 guide articles (11 new this session)
The guide section grew from 2 articles to 13. All are live at `https://fumage.vercel.app/guide`.

